member.summary:
return the ContextInformation that was present when the ConfigurationElement was first deserialized.
if Reset was called, this will be the value of parent.GetOriginalEvaluationContext()
if Reset was not called, this will be the value of this.GetEvaluationContext()

member.remarks:
This property is effectively creating the following instance.
var policy = new RetryExponential( TimeSpan.Zero, TimeSpan.FromSeconds(30), 10);
It is important to note that the retry policy should always honor the so that retry will terminate if the next retry interval will exceed the operation time.

